{
  "stem": "6845.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And what happened there, that too was an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it was also a working camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what happened that in no time I fit in all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was one of the few who spoke German real, real well and [NON-ENGLISH] Kalway-- that I know his name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like you would tell me, I went in my head and took all the unfamiliar-- anyway, and he took to me and used me as an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, if I-- no, I don't even want to what I remember-- that he tried to call me for some offer or what-- for a doctor.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Germany, they used the doctor's wife gets the title too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not like in English, you'll never hear it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Doctor.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he did it maybe not on a regular basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he did do it, which was mind-boggling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was in charge of the sorting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the bloody clothes came in from the German front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the clothes were sorted by-- well, I was in charge so to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there were lots of us together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then it had to go to different places, to the laundry, and fixing, and something,.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it-- it was work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went out from our place to work and came back to sleep in the lager.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we did get to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did we get?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The morning, it was usually brown water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if something swim in it, it was just good luck, some-- I don't know-- maybe a little bit of potato or some vegetable.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was it two or three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
